properties.Name: ProductRestriction
properties.Description: A restriction placed upon the use, procurement, operation or sales of the Product.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: RestrictionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Restriction.

Columns.Name: RestrictedByPartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: RestrictionPeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date that the associated restriction is applied.

Columns.Name: RestrictionPeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date that the associated restriction is applied.

Columns.Name: GoverningStatuteName
Columns.Description: The name of the governing statute.

Columns.Name: GoverningBodyName
Columns.Description: The name of the governing body requiring or invoking the associated restriction.

Columns.Name: ProductRestrictionNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Product Restriction.
